                            <comment id="14408760" author="jdcasey" created="Tue, 13 Sep 2005 13:35:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The specific problem was that the results of merging plugin configurations was not persisted back to the Model instance. It was just a case of switching the referent mergedPlugin to point to the model-based plugin instance rather than the profile-based one.&lt;/p&gt;

